    "rationale": "The credibility assessment team reviewed all 13 credibility factors. Seven factors were formally assessed; all show achieved levels below required levels at MRL 5. Six factors remain not-assessed, representing epistemic gaps. The orphan claim (https://uofa.net/synth/claim/vad-hemolysis-cfd-adequate) was accepted as adequate on the basis of its detailed prose description referencing mesh independence, PIV comparison, and Monte Carlo UQ. The structured evidence derivation chain was not verified prior to acceptance. Decision recorded as Accepted pending resolution of identified gaps in subsequent assessment cycle.",
